data.description: Spacious Hi-Ranch featuring 6 bedrooms and 2 full Baths situated on a large corner lot with a completely fenced yard providing plenty of space to entertain and add a pool. 200 amp electric with solar panels that are owned and an electric car hook up. In addition to being able to park 4 cars, the driveway also features an additional area to park an RV. The property is conveniently located to Tanger Outlets, additional shopping, and major modes of transportation such as the LIE, Southern State, Sagtikos, and LIRR. House being sold AS IS. This one won't last!!!
